section.def:
committee
                (委員會) means the committee of The Society for the
            Relief of Disabled Children;

paragraph.content:
to establish, operate, manage or maintain such homes, clinics and other
                institutions for disabled children or for the curing and rehabilitating of disabled
                children as it may think fit;

to acquire, accept leases of, purchase, take or otherwise hold and enjoy any
                lands, buildings, messuages or tenements of what nature or kind soever and
                wheresoever situate;
